  short_desc => 'If true, DDL operations in READ COMMITTED mode will be executed in a separate DDL transaction instead of the as part of the enclosing transaction block even if ysql_yb_ddl_transaction_block_enabled is true. In other words, for Read Committed, fall back to the mode when ysql_yb_ddl_transaction_block_enabled is false.',
  flags => 'GUC_NOT_IN_SAMPLE',
