  short_desc => 'Used to test yb_index_check()',
  long_desc => 'If set to > 0, number of index rows processed per snapshot is equal to  yb_test_index_check_num_batches_per_snapshot*yb_bnl_batch_size If set to 0, yb_index_check() will execute in single snapshot mode.',
